<text><body>
<cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">三　長老之譬喻二</cb:mulu><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">第十八　拘物頭品</cb:mulu><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一八〇　山古泊達伽（近侍僧團）</cb:mulu><ref cRef="PTS.Ap.191" type="PTS_hide"></ref><cb:div type="other">
<milestone unit="juan" n="19"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0271a08"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0271a09"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">第十九　屈塔奢普毘耶品</cb:mulu><head>第十九　屈塔奢普毘耶品</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0271a10"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0271a11"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0271a12"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一八一　屈塔奢普毘耶（屈塔奢花）</cb:mulu><head>一八一　屈塔奢普毘耶（屈塔奢花）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0271a13"/><p xml:id="pN29p0271a1301">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0271a1301" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>黃金色佛陀，如朝日初昇，巡迴眺四方，直向來風路。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0271a14"/><p xml:id="pN29p0271a1401">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0271a1401" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>屈塔奢花蔓，識認擴伸展，手折其花根，捧獻普沙佛。</l></lg>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0272a" n="0272a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0272a01"/><p xml:id="pN29p0272a0101">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0272a0101" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>依獻其花故，九十二劫間，惡趣吾不知，供佛此果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0272a02"/><p xml:id="pN29p0272a0201">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0272a0201" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>十七劫往昔，三王名開花<note n="0272001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Pupphita（開花）。</note>，大力具七寶，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0272a03"/><p xml:id="pN29p0272a0301">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0272a0301" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0272a04"/><p xml:id="pN29p0272a0401" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者屈塔奢普毘耶長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0272a05"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0272a06"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0272a07"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0272a08"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0272a09"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一八二　槃豆時瓦迦</cb:mulu><head><ref cRef="PTS.Ap.192"></ref>一八二　槃豆時瓦迦</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0272a10"/><p xml:id="pN29p0272a1001">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0272a1001" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>悉達多佛陀，嚴身自存者，深思入靜慮，坐於山谷間。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0272a11"/><p xml:id="pN29p0272a1101">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0272a1101" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>吾往湖最上，索取水草花，最後見盛花，槃豆時瓦迦。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0272a12"/><p xml:id="pN29p0272a1201">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0272a1201" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>兩手吾捧花，拜見大牟尼，清淨吾心喜，捧獻悉達多。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0272a13"/><p xml:id="pN29p0272a1301">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0272a1301" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>捧獻其花故，九十四劫間，惡趣吾不知，供花此果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0272a14"/><p xml:id="pN29p0272a1401">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0272a1401" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>十四劫往昔，統主有一人，其名稱海似<note n="0272001-1" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Samuddakappa（海似）。</note>，大力轉輪王。</l></lg>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0273a" n="0273a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0273a01"/><p xml:id="pN29p0273a0101">六</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0273a0101" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0273a02"/><p xml:id="pN29p0273a0201" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者槃豆時瓦迦長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0273a03"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0273a04"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0273a05"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0273a06"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0273a07"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一八三　庫頓巴利耶</cb:mulu><head>一八三　庫頓巴利耶</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0273a08"/><p xml:id="pN29p0273a0801">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0273a0801" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>輝如黃花樹，佛坐山峽間，如海洋難量，如地不搖動。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0273a09"/><p xml:id="pN29p0273a0901">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0273a0901" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>諸神群參拜，壯牛駿馬如，至人吾親近，雀躍心歡喜。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0273a10"/><p xml:id="pN29p0273a1001">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0273a1001" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>吾採七朶花，裝花滿衣裳，供獻尸棄佛，世間具緣者。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0273a11"/><p xml:id="pN29p0273a1101">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0273a1101" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>捧獻其花故，三十一劫間，惡趣吾不知，供佛此果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0273a12"/><p xml:id="pN29p0273a1201">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0273a1201" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>二十劫往昔，名喚大無過<note n="0273001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Mahānela（大無過）。</note>，大力大威力，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0273a13"/><p xml:id="pN29p0273a1301">六</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0273a1301" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0273a14"/><p xml:id="pN29p0273a1401" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者庫頓巴利耶長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0274a" n="0274a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0274a01"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0274a02"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0274a03"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0274a04"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0274a05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一八四　槃奢哈提耶（五手）</cb:mulu><head><ref cRef="PTS.Ap.193"></ref>一八四　槃奢哈提耶（五手）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0274a06"/><p xml:id="pN29p0274a0601">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0274a0601" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>世間居上首，無上帝沙佛，弟子眾隨後，信步車道來。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0274a07"/><p xml:id="pN29p0274a0701">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0274a0701" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>手持優鉢羅，五花置四朵<note n="0274001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">訂正為 Caturoṭṭhapitā。</note>，以施供祭物，遂行為沈默。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0274a08"/><p xml:id="pN29p0274a0801">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0274a0801" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>黃金色尊佛，遙見來過市，佛身滿光輝，供養兩足尊。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0274a09"/><p xml:id="pN29p0274a0901">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0274a0901" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>吾布施其花，九十二劫間，惡趣吾不知，供佛此果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0274a10"/><p xml:id="pN29p0274a1001">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0274a1001" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>十三劫往昔，其名謂堂認<note n="0274002" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Sabhāsammata（堂認）。</note>，大力具七寶，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0274a11"/><p xml:id="pN29p0274a1101">六</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0274a1101" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0274a12"/><p xml:id="pN29p0274a1201" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者槃奢哈提耶長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0274a13"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0274a14"/>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0275a" n="0275a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0275a01"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0275a02"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0275a03"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0275a04"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0275a05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一八五　依西穆伽達他耶迦（依西穆迦布施）</cb:mulu><head>一八五　依西穆伽達他耶迦（依西穆迦布施）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0275a06"/><p xml:id="pN29p0275a0601">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0275a0601" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>昇輝如朝日，光明如太陽，巴多穆塔拉，如迦休樹光。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0275a07"/><p xml:id="pN29p0275a0701">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0275a0701" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>蜜少不紺青蜜集依西果<note n="0275001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">isimugga 不詳 Mugga 為隱元豆之類。</note><note n="0275002" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">nisandhetvā（異本為 nisantetva, nisanditvā）意義不明。</note>，恰如高樓立，吾施世緣者。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0275a08"/><p xml:id="pN29p0275a0801">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0275a0801" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>彼佛弟子隨，數有八十萬，吾滿彼等鉢，再施更多果。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0275a09"/><p xml:id="pN29p0275a0901">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0275a0901" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>以心清淨故，淨根所使故，十萬劫之間，吾不生惡趣。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0275a10"/><p xml:id="pN29p0275a1001"><ref cRef="PTS.Ap.194"></ref>五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0275a1001" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四萬劫往昔，彼等八人王，大力名地遍<note n="0275003" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Mahisamanta（地徧）。</note>，有為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0275a11"/><p xml:id="pN29p0275a1101">六</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0275a1101" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0275a12"/><p xml:id="pN29p0275a1201" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者依西穆伽達耶迦長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0275a13"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0275a14"/>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0276a" n="0276a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0276a01"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0276a02"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0276a03"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0276a04"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0276a05"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0276a06"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一八六　菩提烏婆塔耶迦（奉事菩提樹）</cb:mulu><head>一八六　菩提烏婆塔耶迦（奉事菩提樹）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0276a07"/><p xml:id="pN29p0276a0701">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0276a0701" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>蘭瑪瓦提市，吾名稱小鼓<note n="0276001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Muraja（小鼓）。</note>，無上菩提樹，常作奉侍事。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0276a08"/><p xml:id="pN29p0276a0801">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0276a0801" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>朝夕盡奉事，淨根所使故，一千八百劫，吾不生惡趣。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0276a09"/><p xml:id="pN29p0276a0901">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0276a0901" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>千五百劫昔，吾為眾人王，其名稱調御<note n="0276002" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Damatha（調御）。</note>，大力轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0276a10"/><p xml:id="pN29p0276a1001">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0276a1001" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0276a11"/><p xml:id="pN29p0276a1101" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者菩提烏婆塔耶迦長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0276a12"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0276a13"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0276a14"/>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0277a" n="0277a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0277a01"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0277a02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一八七　耶伽欽提陀（一思）</cb:mulu><head>一八七　耶伽欽提陀（一思）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0277a03"/><p xml:id="pN29p0277a0301">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0277a0301" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>當一神消逝，壽命盡天界<note n="0277001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">以下至第十一偈前半偈止，於第三二七尼軍提普庇耶長老之處再出。</note>，彼等諸神喜，三聲隨口響：</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0277a04"/><p xml:id="pN29p0277a0401">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0277a0401" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-1em"><l>「尊身往善趣，結交彼諸人，生人為善法，獲得無上信。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0277a05"/><p xml:id="pN29p0277a0501">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0277a0501" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>信植汝善根，確立汝身堅，善宣諸善法，盡身命無搖。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0277a06"/><p xml:id="pN29p0277a0601"><ref cRef="PTS.Ap.195"></ref>四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0277a0601" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>更以身善語，遂行眾多善，再以意為善，慈愍無執著。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0277a07"/><p xml:id="pN29p0277a0701">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0277a0701" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>更多行布施，積福再生因，激勵眾人等，善法與梵行。」</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0277a08"/><p xml:id="pN29p0277a0801">六</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0277a0801" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>諸神以慈愍，賢如天中天，彼等喜尊者：「幾度汝為神？」</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0277a09"/><p xml:id="pN29p0277a0901">七</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0277a0901" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>爾時吾來集，心擾諸神中：「由此吾將沒，吾生何胎中？」</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0277a10"/><p xml:id="pN29p0277a1001">八</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0277a1001" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>制根一沙門，取知吾厭離，彼欲搖吾心，來至吾所居。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0277a11"/><p xml:id="pN29p0277a1101">九</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0277a1101" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>其名須摩那，巴多穆塔拉，教吾義與法，其時吾動搖。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0277a12"/><p xml:id="pN29p0277a1201">一〇</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0277a1201" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>聆聞彼言語，向佛吾心淨，禮敬彼聖賢，忽然吾死逝。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0277a13"/><p xml:id="pN29p0277a1301">一一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0277a1301" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>立地吾再生，淨根所使故，十萬劫往間，吾不墮惡趣。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0277a14"/><p xml:id="pN29p0277a1401">一二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0277a1401" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0278a" n="0278a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0278a01"/><p xml:id="pN29p0278a0101" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者耶伽欽提陀長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0278a02"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0278a03"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0278a04"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0278a05"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0278a06"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一八八　提康尼普毘耶（提康尼花）</cb:mulu><head>一八八　提康尼普毘耶（提康尼花）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0278a07"/><p xml:id="pN29p0278a0701">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0278a0701" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>時吾生為神，圍繞天女群，想起前生業，憶起勝佛陀。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0278a08"/><p xml:id="pN29p0278a0801">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0278a0801" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>提康尼花朶，手執己心淨，捧獻毘婆尸，人中稱長者。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0278a09"/><p xml:id="pN29p0278a0901">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0278a0901" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>吾捧獻供花，九十一劫間，吾不知惡趣，供佛此果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0278a10"/><p xml:id="pN29p0278a1001">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0278a1001" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>七十三劫昔，四人為明王，大力具七寶，有為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0278a11"/><p xml:id="pN29p0278a1101">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0278a1101" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0278a12"/><p xml:id="pN29p0278a1201" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者提康尼普毘耶長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0278a13"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0278a14"/>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0279a" n="0279a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0279a01"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0279a02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一八九　耶迦奢利耶（一行）</cb:mulu><head><ref cRef="PTS.Ap.196"></ref>一八九　耶迦奢利耶（一行）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0279a03"/><p xml:id="pN29p0279a0301">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0279a0301" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>時三十三天，轟然大聲響，吾等為欲縛，佛出於此世。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0279a04"/><p xml:id="pN29p0279a0401">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0279a0401" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>彼等生厭離，如為悲箭刺，吾恃於己力，赴往佛陀前。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0279a05"/><p xml:id="pN29p0279a0501">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0279a0501" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>化作茲整備，手持曼陀羅，於其涅槃時，以此捧獻佛。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0279a06"/><p xml:id="pN29p0279a0601">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0279a0601" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>諸神並天女，爾時向吾謝，十萬劫之間，吾不生惡趣。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0279a07"/><p xml:id="pN29p0279a0701">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0279a0701" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>六萬劫往昔，大力十六人，名喚大力士<note n="0279001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Mahāmallājana（大力士）。</note>，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0279a08"/><p xml:id="pN29p0279a0801">六</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0279a0801" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0279a09"/><p xml:id="pN29p0279a0901" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者耶迦奢利耶長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0279a10"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0279a11"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0279a12"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0279a13"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0279a14"/>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0280a" n="0280a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0280a01"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0280a02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一九〇　提萬提普毘耶（提萬提花）</cb:mulu><head>一九〇　提萬提普毘耶（提萬提花）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0280a03"/><p xml:id="pN29p0280a0301">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0280a0301" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>上座調伏者<note n="0280001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">依暹羅本讀為 theraṁ panijjhāma。</note>，彼等作思惟，大眾來吾前，均非苦熱生。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0280a04"/><p xml:id="pN29p0280a0401">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0280a0401" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>丹瑪達西佛<note n="0280002" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">過去二十四佛之第十五佛。參閱 Jātaka I, P. 38。</note>，彼尊之弟子，名喚須難陀<note n="0280003" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Sunanda（善喜）。</note>，彼亦來吾所。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0280a05"/><p xml:id="pN29p0280a0501">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0280a0501" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>事吾隨從等，爾時與吾花，吾手執其花，獻與佛弟子。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0280a06"/><p xml:id="pN29p0280a0601">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0280a0601" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>立地吾死逝，不為再生來，一千八百劫，猶不生惡趣。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0280a07"/><p xml:id="pN29p0280a0701">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0280a0701" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>千三百劫昔，八人煙標幟<note n="0280004" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Dhūmaketu（煙標幟）。</note>，大力具七寶，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0280a08"/><p xml:id="pN29p0280a0801"><ref cRef="PTS.Ap.197"></ref>六</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0280a0801" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0280a09"/><p xml:id="pN29p0280a0901" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者提萬提普毘耶長老宣唱此等偈。</p>
<lb ed="N" n="0280a10"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0280a11"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0280a12"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0280a13"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0280a14"/>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0281a" n="0281a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0281a01"/><p xml:id="pN29p0281a0101" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">攝頌：</p>
<lb ed="N" n="0281a02"/><lg xml:id="lgN29p0281a0201" type="abnormal"><l style="text-indent:3em">屈塔奢與槃豆特伊、庫頓巴利、哈提耶、</l>
<lb ed="N" n="0281a03"/><l style="text-indent:3em">依西穆伽與菩提、耶伽欽提、提康尼、</l>
<lb ed="N" n="0281a04"/><l style="text-indent:3em">耶迦奢利、提萬提、十人說偈六十二。</l></lg></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0281a05"/>
</cb:div></body></text></TEI>